2026-01-21 11:49:35.756 | INFO     | request_id - a9d6f028-a6ae-406b-8ffa-5e671dc52058 | app.agent.nodes.generate_sql:generate_sql:32 - 生成SQL: SELECT 
    dp.category AS 商品分类,
    SUM(fo.order_amount) AS 销售总额
FROM fact_order fo
JOIN dim_product dp ON fo.product_id = dp.product_id
JOIN dim_date dd ON fo.date_id = dd.date_id
WHERE dd.date_id >= 20250101 AND dd.date_id < 20260101
GROUP BY dp.category
ORDER BY 销售总额 DESC;
